RESOURCE.STRING: Fuel Control Valve Initial Position Setup
Refer to Operation and Maintenance manual for engine start up procedures before operating this test.
Fuel control valve Initial Position Setup will allow the adjustment of the Fuel Control Valves Initial position for when the engine starts
Parameter
Value
Units

Make the desired adjustments and then select Next. Only one adjustment will be allowed at a time. These adjustments will be made once per second. When the adjustment is made the status will notify the next adjustment can be made.
Fuel Control Valve Initial Position
